<topic id="topic_omx_srg_ws">
  <title>Beta 0: Minimum Hardware Requirements</title>
  <body>
    <section id="SupportedConfigs">
      <title>Supported Configurations</title>
      <p>HPE supports the following configurations for HPE Helion <tm tmtype="reg">OpenStack</tm>
        deployment:</p>
      <p>Storage Interconnects/Protocols</p>
      <ul>
        <li>1Gb or 10Gb Eth.</li>
        <li>Software iSCSi</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="HardwareRequirements"><title>Hardware Requirements</title>
      <p>You must have the following hardware configuration:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>1 dedicated NIC for PXE installation. Note: This will disappear in future Beta
          releases.</li>

        <li>2 additional NICs for networking</li>
      </ul>
      <note>For Swift deployment, two disk drives are required on each of the three controller
        nodes.</note>
    </section>
